</p>
<p>Elder Bednar was sustained as a member of the Quorum of the Twelve Apostles of The Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints on October 2, 2004. He subsequently left his position at BYU&ndash;Idaho effective December 1, 2004.</p>
<p>Elder Bednar and his wife, the former Susan K. Robinson, are the parents of three sons.</p>
